title: This....

embed.description: This video teaches you how to jump over walls without needing to jump to wards. The new Katarina makes it so you can place daggers to jump to (similar to wards). Social Media Twitch: http://www.twitch.tv/kat_life Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/KatlifeLoL YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/katlifeee Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/basscaptivesdotori

body:
This sickens me...

All this time, and i never knew this existed...

I genuinely feel ill.

replies.body: 36 sec. When the hell did fruit start spawning there... Every video seen never ever seen one there before
I think its an old video (maybe even PBE), so the fruit was probably in its early stages.

This makes me wonder why Riot didn't set it up so Kat would jump to the ACTUAL DAGGER, and not the edges of the dagger proc area...

Here's hoping they change it.

Yea that baffles me.

It also annoys me that she can Shunpo to you, then walk to the dagger and still get the reset.
I think the reset should only happen when her shunpo target is the actual dagger.
its makes me more ill that fact that you play kat {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-rainbows}}

Haha I don't :P

Although I played her once the other day (to learn how to beat her) went 6/0 in lan, felt dirty as fuck, didn't learn her weakness and then gave up xD

But someone told me about this trick and I had to see if it was a thing....
And it was...
